Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.20,0:23:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貫穿胸膛的七夜匕首
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.00,0:23:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不出口的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.30,0:23:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此甦醒
